show.description: A village girl arrives as a mere substitute bride, but with each passing moment, secrets emerge that have the power to upend lives. In a web of love, betrayal, and political intrigue, the true bride remains a mystery—who will emerge victorious in this high-stakes game? Watch as every hidden truth unfolds, revealing shocking twists at every turn.
